Portia® is dispensed in a blister card containing 28 tablets (see 
                       HOW SUPPLIED
                    ). Portia® may be started using either a Day 1 start or a Sunday start (see Table 3). For the first cycle of a Sunday start regimen, an additional method of contraception should be used until after the first 7 consecutive days of administration.

